data.eml:eml: Molecular phylogeny of Australian Gehyra (Squamata: Gekkonidae) and taxonomic revision of Gehyra variegata in south-eastern Australia

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Sistrom, Mark J., Hutchinson, Mark N., Hutchinson, Rhonda G., Donnellan, Stephen C. (2009): Molecular phylogeny of Australian Gehyra (Squamata: Gekkonidae) and taxonomic revision of Gehyra variegata in south-eastern Australia. Zootaxa 2277: 14-32, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.191131
